<F P=101> Sweden </F>
<H3> <TI>   Expelled Chinese Refugees To Arrive at Arlanda </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0803134294 Stockholm Radio Sweden in Swedish 1130 GMT 8 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0803134294 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Swedish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Taiwan has expelled four refugees from the People's 
Republic of China to Sweden. All four are reported to have 
taken part in the democracy movement and are expected at Arlanda 
[airport] this evening. The reason why Taiwan is expelling the 
four Chinese is that one or more of them are reported to have 
relatives in Sweden. In the past, refugees from the People's 
Republic have been allowed to stay in Taiwan, but as the 
relations between the two countries have improved, interest in 
the refugees has lessened in Taiwan. 

</TEXT>

